{htxt id="allowed-membership-types-title"}
  {ts}Allowed Membership Types{/ts}
{/htxt}
{htxt id="allowed-membership-types"}
{capture assign=membersOnlyEventConfigPath}{crmURL p="civicrm/admin/membersonlyevent"}{/capture}
{ts 1=$membersOnlyEventConfigPath}You can set the membership types that will be able to register participants for this event here. Note that users with a CMS role with the permission "Can register for members only events irrespective of membership status" will be able to register to the event regardless of your setting here. You can also set whether the membership will need to be current either at the time of booking or optionally also at the event start date <a href="%1">here{/ts}</a>
{/htxt}
